    • Constructor Detail

      • HandleResetPasswordRequest

        public HandleResetPasswordRequest(java.lang.String email,
                                  java.lang.String expiryTime,
                                  java.lang.String baseUrl)
        Constructor with the mandatory params to build this object.
        Parameters:
        email - The email address entered by the recipient/user which will be required to generate token for already registered user.
        expiryTime - The duration(in minutes) till which reset password token remains valid E.g. 120 = 2 hours
        baseUrl - The url to redirect the user to web flow (reset password page) where the user can set new password.
